%3Abody_link\" target=\"_blank\">PG</a>) back in October 2024. More specifically, I published an <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725230-procter-and-gamble-buy-the-dip\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725230-procter-and-gamble-buy-the-dip\" target=\"_blank\">article</a> on 10-5-2024 under the title of \"Procter &amp; Gamble: Buy The Dip\u201d on Seeking Alpha. As you</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745450-procter-and-gamble-inventory-does-not-lie-and-points-to-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 02:52:51"}, {"id": "4745456", "title": "The Yen Weakens As The BoJ Holds", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up image of Japanese Yen on a white background\" data-id=\"109835538\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">gaffera</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Min Joo Kang, Senior Economist, South Korea and Japan and Chris Turner, Global Head of Markets and Regional Head of Research for UK &amp; CEE</em></p> <p></p> <h2>A January hike is not a done deal, says Ueda</h2> <p>According to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745456-yen-weakens-as-boj-holds", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 02:50:00"}, {"id": "4745451", "title": "Super Micro Computer's Outlook Is Now A PIPE Dream", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fortunes Lost: Winning Lottery Destroyed by Spill\" data-id=\"157501967\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Saturated/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>GenAI has created incredible opportunities for companies to globally benefit from surging productivity gains and unlocking efficiency. As a result, organizations have demonstrated strong ambitions in investing in and upgrading their technology infrastructure to support</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745451-super-micro-computer-smci-outlook-is-now-a-pipe-dream", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 02:15:59"}, {"id": "4745446", "title": "Rexel SA Facing Challenges, But The Macro Environment Should Be Near The Bottom", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Electrician fixing a fuse box at a house\" data-id=\"2151912557\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"971px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Hispanolistic/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The last six or so months haven\u2019t been the easiest for French electrical products distributor <strong>Rexel SA </strong>(<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RXEEY\" title=\"Rexel S.A.\">OTCPK:RXEEY</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RXLSF\" title=\"Rexel S.A.\">OTCPK:RXLSF</a>). Higher rates have hurt activity in both residential and non-residential construction, and industrial sales have been hit by not</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745446-rexel-sa-facing-challenges-but-the-macro-environment-should-be-near-the-bottom", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:47:39"}, {"id": "4745443", "title": "CAVA: Excellent Same Store Sales Growth Tempered By Ridiculous Price (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Men eating Greek Salad\" data-id=\"1212709124\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JulPo/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>AI software isn't the only sector having a big moment in 2024. Fast-casual restaurant chains, especially those targeting a healthier demographic, are also skyrocketing to new heights in 2024. Sweetgreen (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SG\" title=\"Sweetgreen, Inc.\">SG</a>) and CAVA (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CAVA\" title=\"CAVA Group, Inc.\">CAVA</a></span>) have each seen</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745443-cava-excellent-same-store-sales-growth-tempered-by-ridiculous-price-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:35:45"}, {"id": "4745441", "title": "Enerpac Tool Group Stock Takes A Dive On Q1 Earnings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Labourers Planning on Site\" data-id=\"1917054502\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FatCamera</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>December 18th was a rough day for shareholders of <b>Enerpac Tool Group Corp.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EPAC\" title=\"Enerpac Tool Group Corp.\">EPAC</a></span>). As the broader market plunged following <a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2024/12/18/nx-s1-5230508/federal-reserve-interest-rates-economy-inflation\" rel=\"nofollow\">news</a> that the Federal Reserve would likely only be cutting interest rates twice next year</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745441-enerpac-tool-group-stock-takes-a-dive-on-q1-earnings", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:26:46"}, {"id": "4745440", "title": "Dividend Growers Hedge Against Trump Bump To Inflation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>By Michael Clarfeld, CFA</p> <p>Portfolio Manager, ClearBridge Investments</p> <h2>There Will Be Second-Order Effects to Trump 2.0</h2> <p>Trump won \u2014 buy crypto! Trump won \u2014 buy energy stocks! Trump won and will loosen regulations on financial companies \u2014 buy bank stocks!</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745440-dividend-growers-hedge-against-trump-bump-to-inflation", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:07:31"}, {"id": "4745444", "title": "The GEO Group: Can Benefit On Trump's Mass Deportation Plan, But Stock Is Overvalued", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Prison\" data-id=\"117559713\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3426px\" height=\"2208px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-cr